# Content voice

## Tone

- First person where appropriate (About, Contact)
- Concrete stack: React, Node.js, TypeScript, MongoDB, Tailwind
- No fictional employers (Starbucks, Tesla, Meta template placeholders)

## Projects

- Accurate descriptions and GitHub links
- Tags match real technologies
- Prefer real thumbnails over repeated placeholder images

## Testimonials

- Real quotes and attributions only
- No stock `randomuser.me` avatars; use initials or omit images

## Resume

- Keep `src/utils/resume.js` in sync with `constants` experiences and projects
